554
00:28:20,413 --> 00:28:21,833
Hey, Ko Gyeol!

555
00:28:21,933 --> 00:28:25,100
I can't abandon my beliefs and values.

556
00:28:25,100 --> 00:28:27,333
If he's that firm in his decision,
what can we do?

557
00:28:27,333 --> 00:28:28,400
Cho Seong Jun!

